## ERROR TIPS

### Inventory full when harvesting
- Ensure that the agent's inventory has enough space before attempting to harvest items.

### Could not extract due to missing entity or item
- Before attempting to extract, verify that the target entity exists at the specified location and contains the item to be extracted. The agent is trying to extract iron-plate from (0,0) where there is no such entity.
